---
title: One-Pan Chicken Kale Caesar Wraps with Parmesan & Tomato
description: All hail (or should we say all kale) this 20-minute salad wrap, perfect for a speedy, delicious lunch or dinner! It’s light, creamy, and bursting with crisp textures and satisfying flavors. You’ll quickly sear Italian herbed chicken cutlets while whipping up a lemony, creamy Caesar dressing. Then, it’s time to wrap! Layers of warm, savory chicken, juicy tomato, tender, crunchy dressed kale, and lots of Parmesan mingle in warm tortillas for a mealtime coup the likes of which Brutus would be proud. Et tu, Chef?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/653908c4b8cd6bf4c478f8a6-aa5c1570.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/653908c4b8cd6bf4c478f8a6.pdf
